														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4597200">
									

<p>I haven't yet checked out many pages featuring Rosen beyond the more popular pattern screamer articles, but I'm not entirely convinced this hub is necessary. It seems like information that could all be gleaned by reading the articles themselves, minus the white text, which is also too vague for me to really be invested.</p>
<p>The screamer tales/SCPs I've read seem to follow a pattern of opening with something mundane then having some hidden text be mildly threatening, and the page doesn't really break that format. Not my thing.</p>

